{"tid":146379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人命當垃圾 19個女胚胎棄置地下渠","createTime":"2017-03-07T04:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T06:56:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20ee70ff16c4b26a89173329a49ec253503283bc","tid":146379,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">【恐怖國度】人命當垃圾 19個女胚胎棄置地下渠<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170307/56392499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170307%2F56392499&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2Bh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=323f1194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170307%2F56392499&h=119b02a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170307/56392499</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n印度警方在馬哈拉施特拉邦（Maharashtra）的地下渠，發現19個被遺棄的女胚胎，揭示在重男輕女風氣下，多條無辜小生命被犧牲的慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170306/large/1488795896_13a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170306%2Flarge%2F1488795896_13a8.jpg&h=b8de454a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方是在上周日調查一宗26歲女子墮胎期間死亡案件時，揭發醫生科德普里（Babasaheb Khidrapure）將多個女胚胎包在藍色膠袋內，再遺棄在診所附近的地下渠。科德普里正在潛逃，而涉案丈夫因說服女子墮胎已經被捕。<br />\n<br />\n產前性別檢測在印度屬違法，有所要求的父母，或同意進行有關檢測的醫生，最高可被判監5年。雖然法例是想杜絕重男輕女的父母會在懷上女嬰時墮胎，但有關檢測在當地十分普遍，尤其在偏遠地區。醫學權威雜誌《英國醫學期刊》在2011年的報告指，過去30年就有1,200萬名女嬰，因媽媽選擇墮胎無法降臨世上。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"e49359de0d0cd9a9d94ecdfc06daf229f7bc7b8b","tid":146379,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊才子"},{"pid":"d5515ae9998b15cdd0730dc5ee727eaccf21bca6","tid":146379,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"果然係文明古國一分子"},{"pid":"933e44a40ba334378c62f93f5ba728a1d5a840bf","tid":146379,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"果19個女嬰算好彩 唔洗係d嘢咁嘅垃圾國家生活一世"},{"pid":"e1ab51be22678ffc9c6f894e642a2804db3bef84","tid":146379,"uid":55695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"姐係幾多個月"},{"pid":"ca514adcaab378b03667f07ce60ec96d9f9d2311","tid":146379,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"咁細個都唔識痛架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69daed64ba1a529f2b160e4b77645301cf17e40","tid":146379,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果19個女嬰算好彩 唔洗係d嘢咁嘅垃圾國家生活一世</blockquote><br />\nsad but ture"},{"pid":"db0bcb7c5347061293a2af1778337bd27e9308f4","tid":146379,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果19個女嬰算好彩 唔洗係d嘢咁嘅垃圾國家生活一世</blockquote><br />\n大個左被班畜牲強姦重痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}